title: Rock'n'roll Burger
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Western, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Delivery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A restaurant that serves a variety of fast food, such as burgers, sides, shakes, plus alcohol. The fugazzi burger is vegan, as are a couple of the sides and appetizers, plus you could create your own sandwich. No vegan milkshakes or desserts. Has a pinball machine bar.
